# Images should be placed in this directory
# The website references the following images:
# - logo.png (Logo for navigation bar)
# - professional-image.jpg (About section image)
# - project-1.jpg, project-2.jpg, project-3.jpg (Portfolio project images)

# To add images:
# 1. Download professional images from Google Images, Unsplash, or Pexels
# 2. Save them in this /public directory with the exact filenames above
# 3. The images will automatically be served by Next.js
